data.description: Welcome to this gorgeous, 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom, updated home in Spence Crossing. Centrally located near beach, shopping, schools, interstate, and bases. This home has been well maintained and includes laminate flooring throughout 1st and 2nd floor, updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances and quartz countertops, updated bathrooms, custom electric fireplace with shiplap surround, and custom plantation shutters. The lower level flex room can serve as an office, theater, or 4th bedroom. This home is move in ready and shows true pride of ownership. Enjoy all the beautiful amenities that this community offers. Its low maintenance living at its finest.
